FBIS4-38411 "drsov104_b_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-104 Daily Report 27 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yegorov Replaces Shakhray on Personnel Policy Council Yegorov Replaces Shakhray on Personnel Policy Council LD2705154294 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1440 GMT 27 May 94 LD2705154294 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] [Text] Moscow, 27 May -- Russian Federation President Boris Yeltsin today issued a decree on changes to the Council for Personnel Policy under the Russian president. According to the document, Nikolay Yegorov is replacing Sergey Shakhray on the Council. This follows the president's edict of 16 May relating to the minister for affairs of nationalities and regional policy, the president's press service said.
